SCORE: Display your Rifts character sheet

Syntax: score

DESCRIPTION:
  Displays your full Palladium Rifts character sheet, including:
    - Name, race, alignment, O.C.C. level and experience
    - All eight Palladium attributes (IQ, ME, MA, PS, PP, PE, PB, Spd)
      with derived combat bonuses for each
    - Vitals: HP/SDC for SDC characters, MDC for MDC beings
    - PPE (magic power) and ISP (psionic power) if applicable
    - Active status effects in a boxed panel (Thirst quenched and Stoned show in blue)
    - Combat stats: APM, strike/parry/dodge bonuses, damage bonus

EXAMPLE:
  score

SEE ALSO: skills, spells, psionics, sbar, combat
